{"tid":1228730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為左紀念烈士巴打，我整咗朵白菊花，希望各位可以睇下","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:01:22.000Z","uid":227229,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6c98de20ec17e8c6a2b26e4362abac827f21b2","tid":1228730,"uid":227229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，我第一次開post。啱啱仲要開錯台，對唔住。<br />\n<br />\n我見大家都摺紙鶴同玫瑰。因為我剪剪貼貼比較叻啲，同埋睇到巴絲打話可以用菊花，所以就上網學，用咗張白畫紙整咗朵菊花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HP7CEj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHP7CEj6.png&h=8e2e5f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得個size 大少少會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲醜，但我都想出少少力，希望果位烈士可以安息、一路好走。<br />\n<br />\n摺紙教學：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nAOjxkRHOn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnAOjxkRHOn4&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b8d87d6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nAOjxkRHOn4</a> <br />\n<br />\n各位 辛苦晒啦！"},{"pid":"2ea7bf7052e13da463dccafa8be5a45e6f209119","tid":1228730,"uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:55:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬好有心思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e9ce94a6c918f900e25cfabe2891ea1288b144","tid":1228730,"uid":108201,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"謝謝你，幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef870ee3b32ba610d27422620c93f421b0bfe024","tid":1228730,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"花都唔識摺留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f0eb135997dca502766e94fc252c6337568ed0","tid":1228730,"uid":227229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea7bf7052e13da463dccafa8be5a45e6f209119","tid":1228730,"uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"reply