A%25B1%25E6%258A%2598%25E7%25B4%2599&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=ded00d8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.origami.plus/%E7%99%BE%E5%90%88%E8%8A%B1%E6%8A%98%E7%B4%99</a><br />\n百合花, 可以搵A4紙摺<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2094818310645370?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2094818310645370%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=884a4775\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2094818310645370?sfns=mo</a><br />\n紙巾花, 呢個就超簡單<br />\n手殘都做到"},{"pid":"14606fb5dc8bf5029247817a3048e4b1e2cb6878","tid":1228730,"uid":131431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"26e68473b9b3f2c1c240f3869eace11419475896","tid":1228730,"uid":262491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"樓主整既菊花好靚好有心思!<br />\n想摺玫瑰可以試下依邊。唔同難度都有。手上冇摺紙專用既紙上唔到圖&hellip;&hellip;難度高既唔推薦用A4紙，太脆會摺得多會爛<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.origami-flower.org/howto-origami-rose.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.origami-flower.org%2Fhowto-origami-rose.php&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=fd3ef8a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.origami-flower.org/howto-origami-rose.php</a><br />\n推自己整花。各位手足下晝見"},{"pid":"2b4cc45d6785215f6d0a0ff0bcc750e3202b118f","tid":1228730,"uid":226048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef870ee3b32ba610d27422620c93f421b0bfe024","tid":1228730,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"花都唔識摺留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:43:44.000Z","msg":"可以去YouTube打origami lily easy之類搵下<br />\n簡單有簡單摺 最緊要係份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07576acc63766259ba8e04c478bf4d2a58